<br />\n你自己L未開始先放棄<br />\n<br />\n護士清算左未<br />\n日日角色扮演<br />\n<br />\n有無八ha secre t 死仆街<br />\n訓左無睇吖<br />\n<br />\n615 又開關啦<br />\n又利用醫護喇<br />\n<br />\n正垃圾 醫護罷工<br />\n捍衛自己專業 <br />\n捍衛香港安全<br />\n<br />\n你班死仆街<br />\n自己驚死 唔敢罷工<br />\n開埋工會 比你地加油聚人頭<br />\n喂到入口 死都唔出聲<br />\n唔敢出聲咪airdrop文宣囉<br />\n<br />\n家陣叫你去死哶<br />\n罷工要坐監咩<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n成年人都唔夠學生識衡量價值<br />\n<br />\n垃圾連仔ban9我喇<br />\n我係要周圍痴旮旯<br />\n<br />\n死仆街五毛唔搞日日ban9我<br />\n你最威喇仆街連仔<br />\n連仔死仆街</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"fa3282d185d4ca87f93d910e4262d65f5be9670a","tid":2060451,"uid":58008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fe8b926664b99c7395508d24b243d6592b0a4303","tid":2060451,"uid":73569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1dacb586ac60bbe5404ea97d277dbec20471d414","tid":2060451,"uid":58008,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T15:51:56.000Z","msg":"打就快啦<br />\n屌"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T15:53:31.000Z","msg":"未打前就兇狠<br />\n就打前就會變碌撚"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T16:32:31.000Z","msg":"依家美軍飛台灣都無強烈xx口交<br />\n因為知道真係就打<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40c699d8cde63127ae33bc34429c9e664ff5a064","tid":2060451,"uid":838,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T18:57:01.000Z","msg":"睇嚟佢承認天安門死過人，有過血腥鎮壓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9dea64b3c8139bed2dd799fc94da54ed0d2f711c","tid":2060451,"uid":70487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fa3282d185d4ca87f93d910e4262d65f5be9670a","tid":2060451,"uid":58008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fe8b926664b99c7395508d24b243d6592b0a4303","tid":2060451,"uid":73569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1dacb586ac60bbe5404ea97d277dbec20471d414","tid":2060451,"uid":58008,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T15:51:56.000Z","msg":"打就快啦<br />\n屌"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T15:53:31.000Z","msg":"未打前就兇狠<br />\n就打前就會變碌撚"},"cit